<commentary id="COMT_1101" scriptId="SCRT_1101">
<commentText>此爲書之首篇 故 所記多務本之意 乃入道之門 積德之基 學者之先務也 凡十六章</commentText>
<targetConcept name=" " conceptId=" "/>
<mention personId="PESN_1101" bookId="BOOK_1101"/>
<comtURL>https://ctext.org/dictionary.pl?if=gb&id=89603</comtURL>
</commentary>
<commentary id="COMT_1102" scriptId="SCRT_1101">
<commentText>凡十六章 邢云旣以學爲章首 遂以名篇 </commentText>
<mention text="邢云" quoteId="QUOT_1101" personId="PESN_1102" bookId="BOOK_1102"/>
</commentary>
<commentary id="COMT_1103" scriptId="SCRT_1101">
<commentText>孔子未免身為匹夫五而知天命然後脩先王之 傳諸人以儒自處以好學自稱其恒言曰學而不 厭誨人不倦如學而時習之亦以勸人是雖未足以 畫聖人亦足以槃孔子故以居首嵬輯者之意也荀 子首勤學蓋木諸</commentText>
<mention personId="PESN_1103" bookId="BOOK_1103"/>
</commentary>
<commentary id="COMT_1104" scriptId="SCRT_1102">
<commentText>學之爲言 效也 人性皆善 而覺有先後 後覺者必效先覺之所爲 乃可以明善而復其初也 </commentText>
<targetConcept name="學" conceptId="CNCP_1101"/>
<mention personId="PESN_1101" bookId="BOOK_1101"/>
<comtURL>https://ctext.org/dictionary.pl?if=gb&id=89604</comtURL>
</commentary>
<commentary id="COMT_1104" scriptId="SCRT_1102">
<comtNote>愚謂</comtNote>
<commentText>愚謂及人而樂者 順而易 不知而不慍者 逆而難 故 惟成德者能之 然 德之所以成 亦由學之正, 習之熟, 說之深而不已焉耳</commentText>
<mention personId="PESN_1101" bookId="BOOK_1101"/>
</commentary>
<commentary id="COMT_1105" scriptId="SCRT_1102">
<comtNote>邢曰</comtNote>
<commentText>邢曰稱師曰子_公羊傳曰子沈子 何休云稱子冠氏上者 著其爲師也_直言子曰者 以其聖德著聞 師範來世 不須言其氏 人盡知之也</commentText>
<targetConcept name="子" conceptId="CNCP_1100"/>
<mention text="邢曰_公羊傳曰" quoteId="QUOT_1108" personId="PESN_1102" bookId="BOOK_1102"/>
<comtURL>https://db.itkc.or.kr/dir/item?itemId=MO#/dir/node?dataId=ITKC_MO_0597A_0350_020_0010</comtURL>
</commentary>
<commentary id="COMT_1105" scriptId="SCRT_1102">
<comtNote>補曰</comtNote>
<commentText>補曰 學 受敎也 </commentText>
<targetConcept name="學" conceptId="CNCP_1101"/>
<mention personId="PESN_1102" bookId="BOOK_1102"/>
</commentary>
<commentary id="COMT_1105" scriptId="SCRT_1102">
<comtNote>補曰</comtNote>
<commentText>補曰朋。同道者也_坤卦注_自遠方來則其人必豪傑。致之者亦賢哲也</commentText>
<targetConcept name="朋" conceptId="CNCP_1104"/>
<mention text=" " personId="PESN_1102" bookId="BOOK_1102"/>
</commentary>
<commentary id="COMT_1105" scriptId="SCRT_1102">
<comtNote>補曰</comtNote>
<commentText>補曰君子。有德之稱。</commentText>
<targetConcept name="君子" conceptId="CNCP_1107"/>
<mention text=" " personId="PESN_1102" bookId="BOOK_1102"/>
</commentary>
<commentary id="COMT_1105" scriptId="SCRT_1102">
<comtNote>或曰</comtNote>
<commentText>或曰學者。業道之名</commentText>
<targetConcept name="學" conceptId="CNCP_1101"/>
<mention personId="PESN_1102" bookId="BOOK_1102"/>
</commentary>
<commentary id="COMT_1105" scriptId="SCRT_1102">
<comtNote>駁曰</comtNote>
<commentText>駁曰非也。學記曰人不學。不知道。孔子曰吾十有五志于學。此方是業道之名。</commentText>
<targetConcept name="學" conceptId="CNCP_1101"/>
<mention text="學記曰" quoteId="QUOT_1118" personId="PESN_1102" bookId="BOOK_1102"/>
</commentary>
<commentary id="COMT_1105" scriptId="SCRT_1102">
<comtNote>侃曰</comtNote>
<commentText>侃曰學有三時 一身中時_學記云時過然後學則勤苦而難成_</commentText>
<targetConcept name="時" conceptId="CNCP_1102"/>
<mention text="侃曰_學記云" quoteId="QUOT_1120" personId="PESN_1102" bookId="BOOK_1102"/>
</commentary>
<commentary id="COMT_1105" scriptId="SCRT_1102">
<comtNote>駁曰</comtNote>
<commentText>駁曰非也。時習者。時時習之也_朱子云_</commentText>
<targetConcept name="時習" conceptId="CNCP_1102"/>
<mention text="朱子云" quoteId="QUOT_1123" personId="PESN_1102" bookId="BOOK_1102"/>
</commentary>
<commentary id="COMT_1105" scriptId="SCRT_1102">
<comtNote>王曰</comtNote>
<commentText>王曰學者。以時誦習之</commentText>
<targetConcept name="學" conceptId="CNCP_1101"/>
<mention text="王曰" quoteId="QUOT_1125" personId="PESN_1102" bookId="BOOK_1102"/>
</commentary>
<commentary id="COMT_1105" scriptId="SCRT_1102">
<comtNote>駁曰</comtNote>
<commentText>駁曰非也。誦習而已者。後世之學也。禮樂射御。可習者多。奚但誦而已。易曰朋友講習_兌大象_講者論辨也。無所不包。誦則詩書而已。學止是哉。</commentText>
<targetConcept name="學" conceptId="CNCP_1101"/>
<mention text="易曰" quoteId="QUOT_1126" personId="PESN_1102" bookId="BOOK_1102"/>
</commentary>
<commentary id="COMT_1105" scriptId="SCRT_1102">
<comtNote>〔引證〕</comtNote>
<commentText>引證 大戴禮曰君子旣學之。患其不博也。旣博之。患其不習也_曾子立事篇_</commentText>
<targetConcept name="君子" conceptId="CNCP_1107"/>
<mention text="大戴禮曰" quoteId="QUOT_1127" personId="PESN_1102" bookId="BOOK_1102"/>
</commentary>
<commentary id="COMT_1105" scriptId="SCRT_1102">
<comtNote>駁曰</comtNote>
<commentText>包曰同門曰朋 駁曰非也 </commentText>
<targetConcept name="朋" conceptId="CNCP_1104"/>
<mention text="包曰" quoteId="QUOT_1128" personId="PESN_1102" bookId="BOOK_1102"/>
</commentary>
<commentary id="COMT_1105" scriptId="SCRT_1102">
<comtNote>何曰</comtNote>
<commentText>何曰凡人有所不知。君子不怒_邢云古之學者爲己。含章內映。他人不知。而我不怒也。一云若有人鈍根不能知解者。君子恕之而不怒也_</commentText>
<targetConcept name="不慍" conceptId="CNCP_1106"/>
<mention text="何曰" quoteId="QUOT_1132" personId="PESN_1102" bookId="BOOK_1102"/>
</commentary>
<commentary id="COMT_1105" scriptId="SCRT_1102">
<comtNote>或曰</comtNote>
<commentText>或曰夫子一生。學不厭敎不倦。此正指誨人一節。故魏文靖講學余山。有學者辨論不釋。怫形于色。文靖曰人不自知。于我何慍。正得此意</commentText>
<targetConcept name="學" conceptId="CNCP_1101"/>
<mention text="文靖曰" quoteId="QUOT_1133" personId="PESN_1102" bookId="BOOK_1102"/>
</commentary>
<commentary id="COMT_1105" scriptId="SCRT_1102">
<comtNote>駁曰</comtNote>
<commentText>駁曰非也。此章乃成己成物之全體。首節成己之事也。旣成己矣。人知之而從我則樂。人不知之而不宗我則不慍。明成物之權。不在己也。邢氏鈍根之說。豈足述乎</commentText>
<mention personId="PESN_1102" bookId="BOOK_1102"/>
</commentary>
<commentary id="COMT_1106" scriptId="SCRT_1102">
<commentText>子為男子美稱 亦為大夫之稱 古者天子世嗣 諸侯世嗣 大夫不世爵 士不世官 </commentText>
<targetConcept name="子" conceptId="CNCP_1100"/>
<mention text="古者" quoteId="QUOT_1134" personId="PESN_1103"/>
</commentary>
<commentary id="COMT_1106" scriptId="nan">
<commentText>朋 黨類 謂從我游者也 樂 謂樂其在我者 而不復它求也 學成面孚於人 遠方士亦有來從我游者 我教而育之 亦以在我者已 是其可樂之至 豈復有所慊而它求乎 </commentText>
<targetConcept name="朋" conceptId="CNCP_1104"/>
<mention personId="PESN_1103"/>
</commentary>
<commentary id="COMT_1107" scriptId="SCRT_1103">
<commentText>有子 孔子弟子 名若 善事父母爲孝 善事兄長爲弟</commentText>
<targetConcept name="有子"/>
<mention personId="ANNO_1101" bookId="BOOK_1101"/>
</commentary>
