<commentText>此言人能孝弟 則其心和順 少好犯上 必不好作亂也</commentText>
<mention personId="ANNO_1101" bookId="BOOK_1101"/>
</commentary>
<commentary id="COMT_1107" scriptId="nan">
<commentText>務 專力也 </commentText>
<targetConcept name="務"/>
<mention personId="ANNO_1101" bookId="BOOK_1101"/>
</commentary>
